263
00:22:24,092 --> 00:22:26,511
Then the two of us...

264
00:22:38,982 --> 00:22:40,442
I agree

265
00:22:43,111 --> 00:22:43,945
Yeah

266
00:22:45,614 --> 00:22:47,115
That's right.

267
00:22:48,033 --> 00:22:50,077
It's my life.

268
00:22:51,787 --> 00:22:52,704
Yeah

269
00:22:53,246 --> 00:22:55,665
(Erika) It's okay for me to be happy.

270
00:22:57,626 --> 00:22:58,668
Of course

271
00:23:01,671 --> 00:23:05,342
Thank you, Yukiya-san is really kind.

272
00:23:06,093 --> 00:23:08,261
-(Yukiya) I guess so.-(Erika) That's right.

273
00:23:11,056 --> 00:23:12,557
...If so⸺

274
00:23:13,767 --> 00:23:16,019
Is that my mother's blood?

275
00:24:04,693 --> 00:24:05,861
(sound of door opening)

276
00:24:07,154 --> 00:24:09,614
(Hanaho) I'm going to take a bath.

277
00:24:09,698 --> 00:24:10,824
(Masayuki) Yeah

278
00:24:14,536 --> 00:24:17,914
Um... Masayuki-san

279
00:24:18,874 --> 00:24:19,833
(Masayuki) Huh?

280
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:24,087
Me today...

281
00:24:25,046 --> 00:24:26,715
On the scheduled date...

282
00:24:27,382 --> 00:24:30,343
I'd like you to stay awake if you like.

283
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:34,472
please

284
00:24:34,556 --> 00:24:39,019
I've already been told a lot of things and I'm at my limit.

285
00:24:42,272 --> 00:24:46,526
Do you know what kind of situation I'm in right now?

286
00:24:47,611 --> 00:24:48,445
(Hanaho) Huh...

287
00:24:50,113 --> 00:24:51,281
Are you tired?

288
00:24:51,364 --> 00:24:54,075
I'm in charge of everything about the space business.

289
00:24:54,576 --> 00:24:58,538
I should know, right? That's what happens when you're the president's wife.

290
00:24:59,706 --> 00:25:00,790
(Hanaho) Ah...

291
00:25:01,583 --> 00:25:02,542
(clicks tongue)

292
00:25:08,757 --> 00:25:11,801
(Masayuki) If you can't rest at home, where should you go?

293
00:25:17,974 --> 00:25:22,979
(sound of second hand)

294
00:25:30,737 --> 00:25:35,742
(tap sound)

295
00:26:21,788 --> 00:26:25,041
It's almost there, Mom.

296
00:26:30,088 --> 00:26:32,841
(Masayuki) 6 days left until the press conference?

297
00:26:36,678 --> 00:26:38,096
Also from “New York Times” and “Reuters”⸺

298
00:26:38,179 --> 00:26:40,223
Looks like I've received an interview request.

299
00:26:40,307 --> 00:26:41,516
(Seiichiro) Ah

300
00:26:42,684 --> 00:26:48,023
If this business is successful, the Ise Zaibatsu will be among the top in the world.

301
00:26:48,481 --> 00:26:49,566
(Seiichiro) I guess so.

302
00:26:49,649 --> 00:26:55,322
(cough cough)

303
00:26:55,405 --> 00:26:56,489
(Masayuki) Are you okay?

304
00:26:56,573 --> 00:26:58,867
It's no big deal.

305
00:26:58,950 --> 00:27:02,537
(cough cough)

306
00:27:06,291 --> 00:27:09,252
After all, wouldn't it be better to have surgery?

307
00:27:10,628 --> 00:27:12,672
What will you do for work in the meantime?

308
00:27:12,756 --> 00:27:15,050
-(Masayuki) That's me... -(Seiichiro) Don't worry.

309
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:20,055
My only regret is that I have no heir.

310
00:27:22,015 --> 00:27:23,642
I asked for it

311
00:27:25,852 --> 00:27:30,231
It's okay, I don't want my dad to worry.

312
00:27:31,691 --> 00:27:32,776
Huh...

313
00:27:32,859 --> 00:27:33,902
(cough cough)

314
00:27:56,508 --> 00:28:01,680
English)

315
00:28:04,641 --> 00:28:07,102
What are your future plans?

316
00:28:07,769 --> 00:28:10,313
Is there a French restaurant you'd like to take me to?

317
00:28:10,397 --> 00:28:11,356
Are you going?

318
00:28:11,439 --> 00:28:13,191
(Men) Please...

319
00:28:13,274 --> 00:28:14,526
(Kyoko) Are you guys going?

320
00:28:14,609 --> 00:28:16,611
What clothes are you using for the next poster?

321
00:28:17,153 --> 00:28:19,239
- (Kumaki) This is it - (Satoshi) Oh?

322
00:28:19,781 --> 00:28:21,825
No, move this, you won't be able to see it!

323
00:28:21,908 --> 00:28:23,159
(Kotoko) Yes, I'm sorry.

324
00:28:23,243 --> 00:28:24,411
I can't use it

325
00:28:47,851 --> 00:28:48,935
(Yukiya as a child) Baishuu?

326
00:28:49,018 --> 00:28:50,353
Yeah

327
00:28:50,895 --> 00:28:54,107
There's a big company called Ise Group.

328
00:28:54,190 --> 00:28:58,236
I decided to protect my mother's factory.

329
00:28:58,319 --> 00:29:00,447
(Yukiya as a child) Hmm, you're so kind.

330
00:29:04,033 --> 00:29:05,994
-(Saori) Yukiya-(Yukiya) Yeah?

331
00:29:06,619 --> 00:29:08,246
Instead of that⸺

332
00:29:08,872 --> 00:29:12,792
Mom has to quit this factory.

333
00:29:13,543 --> 00:29:16,921
why? This is your mother's factory, right?

334
00:29:17,922 --> 00:29:19,507
Hmm...

335
00:29:20,508 --> 00:29:24,637
It might still be a bit difficult for Yukiya, though.

336
00:29:24,721 --> 00:29:26,139
I have no choice

337
00:29:27,348 --> 00:29:32,520
To protect everyone who worked here and this factory.

338
00:29:33,188 --> 00:29:35,648
So what will happen to your mother?

339
00:29:37,650 --> 00:29:41,529
That's right, what should I do?

340
00:29:48,703 --> 00:29:53,041
Ah... it's okay, everything will be fine.

341
00:29:54,417 --> 00:30:00,298
If Yukiya made a face like that, even my mother would start crying.

342
00:30:03,801 --> 00:30:06,513
Are you okay?

343
00:30:07,597 --> 00:30:09,599
- (Male) Oh, no, I have to go... - (Yukiya) Mom!

344
00:30:09,682 --> 00:30:11,809
-(Yukiya) Mother! Mother! -(Male) It's dangerous! It's dangerous!

345
00:30:11,893 --> 00:30:13,728
-(Male) Come back! Come back-(Yukiya) Mom!

346
00:30:13,811 --> 00:30:15,563
- (Male) It's dangerous, it's dangerous - (Yukiya) Mother!

347
00:30:15,647 --> 00:30:17,482
-(Male) No-(Yukiya) Mom!

348
00:30:17,565 --> 00:30:19,234
-(Male) Don't go, no... -(Yukiya) Mom!

349
00:30:20,151 --> 00:30:22,320
-(Yukiya) Mother! -(Male) No.

350
00:30:22,946 --> 00:30:24,864
(Yukiya) Mother Mother

351
00:30:24,948 --> 00:30:26,908
-(Male) No!-(Yukiya) Mom!

352
00:30:40,588 --> 00:30:42,882
(Seiichiro) He is the son of the former president of Matsushima Electric.

353
00:30:44,175 --> 00:30:47,512
I had no relatives so I decided to take him in.

354
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:52,183
(Yukiya) Wait, what about your mother?

355
00:30:52,809 --> 00:30:54,769
give me back my mom

356
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:58,982
Be careless! Who are you talking to? ?

357
00:31:01,025 --> 00:31:02,652
Your mother is⸺

358
00:31:03,486 --> 00:31:07,782
She was leering at my husband and begging for money.

359
00:31:07,865 --> 00:31:10,451
Years and years!

360
00:31:12,662 --> 00:31:17,250
What do you mean by not knowing your own position?

361
00:31:18,626 --> 00:31:22,046
It's your mother's fault!

362
00:31:22,881 --> 00:31:27,635
(Satoshi as a child) Oh no, you'll do anything for a woman's money.

363
00:31:27,719 --> 00:31:29,387
(Masayuki from childhood) The very fact that you were born into this world⸺

364
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:32,932
It was an accident! accident! (kicking sound)

365
00:31:33,016 --> 00:31:35,977
(Satoshi) Hey, accident, accident, accident (sound of kicking)

366
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:37,228
(Masayuki) Shit!

367
00:31:37,729 --> 00:31:39,063
(Satoshi) Orya

368
00:31:39,147 --> 00:31:40,231
(sound of tapping on desk)

369
00:31:55,079 --> 00:31:57,999
(Yukiya) What the Ise Group has done so far⸺

370
00:31:58,082 --> 00:32:00,877
Evidence of numerous fraudulent transactions.

371
00:32:01,586 --> 00:32:05,965
I've endured all this time to spread this

372
00:32:07,425 --> 00:32:12,430
I worked under them even though I was called a sweeper.

373
00:32:18,144 --> 00:32:20,647
I'll finish everything tomorrow

374
00:32:28,112 --> 00:32:29,530
(Yukiya) Then⸺

375
00:32:31,532 --> 00:32:32,909
Two people...

376
00:32:47,131 --> 00:32:48,549
(sound of glass breaking)

377
00:33:03,856 --> 00:33:09,028
(mobile phone vibrator)

378
00:33:18,246 --> 00:33:19,455
hello

379
00:33:28,548 --> 00:33:30,967
-(Yukiya) Hanaho-san! -(Doctor) Excuse me.

380
00:33:33,136 --> 00:33:35,263
(Yukiya) Why... why are you like this...

381
00:33:36,097 --> 00:33:39,726
Brother, brother, where are you?

382
00:33:40,393 --> 00:33:43,354
footsteps)

383
00:33:43,438 --> 00:33:45,398
Ah Erika

384
00:33:46,983 --> 00:33:48,860
-(Yukiya) Erika... -(Erika) Yukiya-san

385
00:33:52,739 --> 00:33:55,825
You know, me...

386
00:33:58,703 --> 00:34:00,455
Are you pregnant?

387
00:34:05,793 --> 00:34:07,712
Child with Masayuki

388
00:34:16,596 --> 00:34:20,099
I know it's not right

389
00:34:20,183 --> 00:34:23,311
But I'm sorry

390
00:34:23,853 --> 00:34:27,940
This was the only way for my happiness

391
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:30,276
Hehe...

392
00:34:31,068 --> 00:34:36,574
I... I'm really the worst person, right?

393
00:34:38,951 --> 00:34:41,579
I can't control my feelings

394
00:34:43,039 --> 00:34:44,957
About Yukiya too

395
00:34:47,585 --> 00:34:49,337
Also about your sister-in-law

396
00:34:50,588 --> 00:34:52,465
I hurt you

397
00:35:00,056 --> 00:35:04,894
But that's why I'm doing this...

398
00:35:06,312 --> 00:35:07,980
I want to guess

399
00:35:15,822 --> 00:35:17,031
sorry

400
00:35:19,534 --> 00:35:24,163
Sorry, wait a minute... What were you saying earlier?

401
00:35:25,414 --> 00:35:26,249
Huh?

402
00:35:26,332 --> 00:35:28,501
(Yukiya) I don't understand at all.

403
00:35:28,584 --> 00:35:31,879
yes? Just as words

404
00:35:36,884 --> 00:35:39,887
There's only one thing I'm asking for

405
00:35:42,014 --> 00:35:43,808
break up with me

406
00:35:47,353 --> 00:35:48,729
With me⸺

407
00:35:50,773 --> 00:35:52,525
please divorce

408
00:35:57,613 --> 00:35:59,323
What do you mean?

409
00:36:01,659 --> 00:36:05,121
If you don't break up with me, I'll tell my father-in-law.

410
00:36:12,753 --> 00:36:14,922
what you are planning

411
00:36:31,105 --> 00:36:36,110
footsteps)

412
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:49,665
I deleted everything

413
00:36:52,668 --> 00:36:55,922
There's no way you can crush the Ise family.

414
00:36:58,132 --> 00:37:00,426
my Ise family

415
00:37:04,847 --> 00:37:07,516
Shut up and disappear

416
00:37:08,684 --> 00:37:12,021
for my happy life

417
00:37:12,104 --> 00:37:14,106
‪♪～

418
00:37:23,991 --> 00:37:24,867
daddy

419
00:38:06,284 --> 00:38:08,452
(Yukiya) I will never forgive you

420
00:38:10,371 --> 00:38:12,373
No matter how many years it takes...

421
00:38:12,456 --> 00:38:14,709
‪～♪

422
00:38:14,792 --> 00:38:16,627
I'll take revenge

423
00:38:19,922 --> 00:38:22,675
 (Seiichiro) Could you please cut ties with the Ise family?

424
00:38:22,758 --> 00:38:23,676
(Yukiya) What I've done so far⸺

425
00:38:23,759 --> 00:38:25,469
Compared to the gravity of the crime

426
00:38:25,553 --> 00:38:27,471
Cheers to these two poor people
